---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Bead Fanatic - Your Bead & Jewellery Making Community"
  description="Learn about Bead Fanatic's mission to connect bead enthusiasts, provide expert guidance, and support the global jewellery making community."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-secondary/10">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-20">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-block mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-2xl">
              <span class="text-white text-2xl">üíñ</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-dark mb-6">
            About Bead Fanatic
          </h1>
          
          <p class="text-xl text-text-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Connecting passionate bead enthusiasts and jewellery makers 
            through knowledge, community, and shared creativity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Story Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-dark mb-6">Our Story</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="prose max-w-none">
          <div class="card">
            <p class="text-lg text-text mb-6">
              Bead Fanatic was born from a passion for the art and craft of beadwork. 
              Having run a physical bead shop for years, we experienced firsthand the 
              joy and challenges that come with this beautiful hobby.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-text mb-6">
              We noticed that while the beading community is incredibly passionate and 
              supportive, there was a gap in easily accessible, comprehensive information. 
              Too often, we'd see customers struggling to identify mystery beads, 
              searching for reliable suppliers, or feeling overwhelmed by the vast 
              world of beading techniques.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-text mb-6">
              That's when we decided to create something special - a digital hub that 
              combines the warmth of our old shop with the power of modern technology. 
              Bead Fanatic is our way of sharing decades of experience and connecting 
              makers around the world.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-text">
              Whether you're trying to identify a vintage bead, looking for your next 
              tutorial, or searching for the perfect supplier, we're here to help you 
              on your beading journey.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <section class="py-20">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-dark mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-text-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            We believe that everyone should have access to the knowledge and 
            resources they need to create beautiful, meaningful jewellery.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="card text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-white text-2xl">üîç</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Identify & Discover</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light">
              Help makers identify unknown beads and discover new types through 
              our comprehensive database and AI-powered tools.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary to-accent rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-dark text-2xl">üéì</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Educate & Inspire</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light">
              Provide clear, detailed tutorials and educational content that 
              empowers makers of all skill levels to learn and grow.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-primary rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-white text-2xl">üåê</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Connect & Support</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light">
              Foster a global community of makers and connect them with 
              reliable suppliers and fellow enthusiasts.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Values Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-dark mb-6">What We Value</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-white text-xl">‚ú®</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2">Quality & Authenticity</h3>
                <p class="text-text-light">
                  We're committed to providing accurate information, verified suppliers, 
                  and genuine expertise. Every piece of content is carefully researched 
                  and reviewed.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary to-accent rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-dark text-xl">üå±</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2">Inclusivity & Accessibility</h3>
                <p class="text-text-light">
                  Beading is for everyone, regardless of skill level, background, or 
                  physical ability. We strive to make our content accessible and 
                  welcoming to all.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-primary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-white text-xl">üìö</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2">Continuous Learning</h3>
                <p class="text-text-light">
                  The world of beading is constantly evolving. We're committed to 
                  staying current with new techniques, materials, and trends while 
                  preserving traditional knowledge.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-dark rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-white text-xl">üë•</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-2">Community First</h3>
                <p class="text-text-light">
                  Our community is at the heart of everything we do. We listen to 
                  feedback, respond to needs, and celebrate the amazing creations 
                  of our members.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Team Section -->
    <section class="py-20">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-dark mb-6">Behind the Scenes</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-text-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            While Bead Fanatic may be digital, it's powered by real people 
            with genuine passion for the craft.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white text-3xl">üë©‚Äçüé≠</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Passionate Makers</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light mb-6">
            Our team combines decades of hands-on beading experience with 
            modern technology skills. We've been where you are - struggling 
            with techniques, hunting for supplies, and celebrating those 
            "eureka!" moments when a project comes together perfectly.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-light">
            Every tutorial we write, every supplier we verify, and every 
            feature we build comes from real experience and genuine 
            understanding of what makers need.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Contact CTA -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Join Our Community
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Ready to be part of something special? Whether you're a beginner 
          or an expert, there's a place for you in the Bead Fanatic community.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/identify" class="btn bg-white text-primary hover:bg-accent transition-colors text-lg px-8 py-4">
            Try Our Bead Identifier
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">
            Get in Touch
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>